Instead  we create camel configuration class

@Configuration
public class CamelConfiguration  {

    @Bean
    public JmsComponent artemis(@Qualifier("artemis") ConnectionFactory cf) {
          JmsComponent jms=new JmsComponent();
          jms.setConnectionFactory(cf);
          return jms;
    }

}

This is the setup that is used in the case we have several connectionfactories, for example this might happen when we connect several different mq Brokers like several artemis instances or
